@node "What is it?" "What is it?"
This program gives you access to the mouse pointer position.

I use a rather large Workbench (1400x1000) and I find it VERY convenient to be
able to get a shell to pop up at my current mouse position.

Combined with ToolsDaemon by Nico François, a shell could pop up by pressing a
shortcut like <CTRL s>.

- Just great, in my own oppinion.. ;)
@endnode

@node "Files" "Files"
